ygData.messageBody:
I was mostly just curious as to what zone and guessed Karnors since so many
are camping that place.

Funny thing is after 51 levels you'd think these train monkies would have
learned how to pull - but no. The same "names" that are pulling the trains
in Karnors are the ones we saw training the zone in SolB, Lower G, CT,
Unrest, Befallen, Old Paw, Blackburrow & Crunchbone.

Sylly
